My meme

My meme comes from the other website to explore the history of baker station.

library(magick)
b165 <- image_read("http://assets.londonist.com/uploads/2012/10/bakerstreet.jpg")%>%
  image_resize("400x400!")
now <- image_read("https://i.redd.it/baker-street-tube-station-platforms-for-transport-for-v0-13dgnb1qdxl81.jpg?s=89ccc2fbf69990a39b0196dad1d9ec69c58a733d")%>%
  image_resize("400x400!")

height_1 <- image_blank(width = 400, height = 400, color = "white") %>%
  image_annotate(text = 'Baker Station in 1863', color = "black", size = 50, font = "Impact", gravity = "center")

height_2 <- image_blank(width = 400, height = 400, color = "black") %>%
  image_annotate(text = 'Baker Station in now', color = "white", size = 50, font = "Impact", gravity = "center")

top <- image_append(c(b165, height_1))
bottom <- image_append(c(now, height_2))

height_meme <- c(top, bottom) %>%
  image_append(stack = TRUE) %>%
  image_scale(800)

  image_write(height_meme ,"my_meme.png")

##My animation GIF My animation GIF is to compare the picture of baker station in different years.
